commit.message:
ci: fix codecov upload on Windows (#30)

`curl` fails on the Windows job, e.g.:

> curl: (23) Failed writing body (0 != 9771)

https://travis-ci.com/pdbpp/fancycompleter/jobs/249344620#L134-L141

Fixed in later curl, redirecting it to a file seems to work around this (https://github.com/curl/curl/issues/3175).
